<item>
            <title>[SOLR-17091] Fix cloud.sh to ignore -slim.tgz</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-17091</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The change that brought us &amp;#45;slim.tgz seems to have broken cloud.sh, because cloud.sh was relying on a single file matching with &apos;solr-*.tgz&apos; existing in the packaging/build/distributions directory&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The forthcoming patch will fix this by ignoring -slim.tgz&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If someone wants to use cloud.sh to test with -slim we can add an option to do that later.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
